"{\"uid\": \"oregonlive.com-living-2024-06-oregon-wool-featured-in-team-usas-blazers-for-2024-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Shaniko Wool Company  The world's first look at Team USA during the opening ceremony of the2024 Paris Olympic and Paralympic Gameswill also shine a spotlight on Oregon sheep ranchers who provided wool for the athletes' blazers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998908606, \"rank\": 1.0914265070591079e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9999979223638302, \"rank\": 1.7575960418213048e-06, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is not theShaniko Wool Company'sfirst time to the parade.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rancher and yarn producer Jeanne Carver intiny Maupinremembers Olympic uniform company Ralph Lauren's initial contact with her.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\", \"score\": 0.9997054159412556, \"rank\": 0.00029450727473646286, \"text\": \"Jeanne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\"}, {\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}, {\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9996891789576362, \"rank\": 0.0003109176822649396, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was in 2012, during thecontroversy created by Team USA's London Games uniformsbeing made in China.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999915427798284, \"rank\": 8.392952372186468e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999891486861404, \"rank\": 9.793505009889378e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not believe\\\" when they called, she said.\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I figured that actually doing business with them would probably never happen.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe I said, 'Things like this do not happen to people like us,'\\\" referring to the ranches that make up the Shaniko Wool Company.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaniko\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Ralph Lauren company placed an order, \\\"it was beyond anything I could have dreamed about,\\\" Carver said.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9996891789576362, \"rank\": 0.0003109176822649396, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it's still just as exciting today as it was then.\\\"\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The remotely located company, named after the nearbyShaniko ghost town, has grown to include 10 ranches in the western U.S. that collectively shear about 500,000 pounds of Merino wool each year, said Carver.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999961969474055, \"rank\": 3.0707941489169736e-06, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Merino wool\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\"}, {\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company also provided wool for the 2022 Winter Olympics in Beijing, and Carver's family property, Imperial Stock Ranch, supplied wool for the 2014 Winter Olympics in Sochi, Russia, and 2018 Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang, South Korea.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999770015558951, \"rank\": 2.285139563413167e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}, {\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9829414714474103, \"rank\": 0.015871192608072394, \"text\": \"Imperial\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9938881500416461, \"rank\": 0.006149434367656574, \"text\": \"Sochi\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999410752043, \"rank\": 4.826703855717909e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"score\": 0.999701498873128, \"rank\": 0.0002985902561585624, \"text\": \"Pyeongchang\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.999999955205568, \"rank\": 4.4788205416378004e-08, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time the Oregon ranchers have contributed to Team USA's summer uniforms.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9999979223638302, \"rank\": 1.7575960418213048e-06, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wool uniforms in summer does not surprise Carver.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said people who have worked closely with sheep for generations, especially those near Shaniko, once deemed the \\\"Wool Capital of the World,\\\"know that the natural material is the original performance fiber and a premier fiber for year-round use.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.973303180980594, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaniko\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Wool not only supports our 'life energy' in a way no other fiber does, it makes the best suiting fabric in the world,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ralph Lauren company has been an official outfitter of Team USA nine times, and all apparel worn by U.S. athletes during official Olympic and Paralympic ceremonies is made in the United States.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9996891789576362, \"rank\": 0.0003109176822649396, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999372744262, \"rank\": 6.272399291388483e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Team USA members will wear a single-breasted navy blazer with red-and-white tipping along with a blue-and-white striped Oxford shirt, blue jeans and cream-colored suede buck lace-up shoes for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2267, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oxford shirt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company contacted Carver 16 months ago about its tailored blazers with these specific requirements:  \\\"We had exactly what they needed,\\\" said Carver, whose family has been raising sheep, cattle, grains and hay on the Imperial Stock Ranch for 153 years.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}, {\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}, {\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9829414714474103, \"rank\": 0.015871192608072394, \"text\": \"Imperial\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The ranchers of Shaniko Wool Company have been working on genetic improvements in their sheep for a very long time.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2635, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaniko\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaniko,_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a group, we are raising some of the finest Merino wool produced in North America.\\\"\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Merino wool\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merino\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1999, when U.S. sheep producers felt pressure from imports, Carver found a new way to market: Convert the greasy wool into wool yarns.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2885, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fifteen years later, Oregon wool helped dress Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9999979223638302, \"rank\": 1.7575960418213048e-06, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was Ralph Lauren's first Made in America Team USA uniform effort,\\\" said Carver.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9996891789576362, \"rank\": 0.0003109176822649396, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 3070, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they told our story, naming us for the first time.\\\"\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carver said she will be watching as Team USA competes at theParis Olympic Games July 26-Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3203, \"end\": 3211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999940975709731, \"rank\": 5.898628442229857e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a powerful emotional experience\\\" for the athletes, she said, \\\"and it's the highest honor to have our fiber worn by these sport legends as they embark on their Olympic journey.\\\"\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Janet Eastman | 503-294-4072  jeastman@oregonian.com|@janeteastman  Janet Eastman has traveled the world covering design shows and interviewing the most famous architects, interior designers and product designers.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3450, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999998103704, \"rank\": 1.8772048937765132e-10, \"text\": \"Janet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 3456, \"end\": 3463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kodak\", \"score\": 0.9999988785968447, \"rank\": 9.053352878369305e-07, \"text\": \"Eastman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kodak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kodak\"}, {\"begin\": 3518, \"end\": 3523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999998103704, \"rank\": 1.8772048937765132e-10, \"text\": \"Janet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 3524, \"end\": 3531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kodak\", \"score\": 0.9999988785968447, \"rank\": 9.053352878369305e-07, \"text\": \"Eastman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kodak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.